{"tid":1922603,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"TOP 10 現金儲備公司","createTime":"2020-03-12T16:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T21:46:41.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8bc66e5633b415f176b29d7ac389f6c850a13b06","tid":1922603,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/finance/transform/55/w550h305/20191108/ac10-ihyxcrq5268806.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ffinance%2Ftransform%2F55%2Fw550h305%2F20191108%2Fac10-ihyxcrq5268806.png&h=6ad9be0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIn spite of wider economic and political uncertainty, American companies are sitting on piles of cash. The world&rsquo;s most cash-rich company, <span style=\"color: red;\">Microsoft currently has the largest cash pile at $136.6 billion as of last quarter</span>. Microsoft&rsquo;s mountain of money is greater than the foreign cash reserves of Indonesia ($128 billion) or Poland ($126 billion).<br />\n<br />\nWarren Buffett&rsquo;s Berkshire Hathaway, Google parent company Alphabet, Apple, and Facebook occupy the other top spots, with $128.2 billion, $121.2 billion, $100.6 billion, and $52.3 billion, respectively. The top five hold a collective $538.9 billion.<br />\n<br />\nFacebook, Amazon, Ford, Oracle, Cisco, and Bristol-Myers round out the rest of the top 10 list. These figures include the company&rsquo;s <span style=\"color: red;\">cash balance as well as its short-term investments such as bonds</span>.<br />\n<br />\nThe top 10 US companies with the most cash on hand<br />\n<br />\n1. Microsoft: $136.6 billion<br />\n2. Berkshire Hathaway: $128.2 billion<br />\n3. Alphabet: $121.2 billion<br />\n4. Apple: $100.6 billion<br />\n5. Facebook: $52.3 billion<br />\n6. Amazon: $43.7 billion<br />\n7. Ford: $37.3 billion<br />\n8. Oracle: $35.7 billion<br />\n9. Cisco: $33.4 billion<br />\n10. Bristol-Myers: $32.5 billion<br />\n<br />\nEvercore的Lee Horowitz表示，作為應對周期性低迷的一種方式，科技公司尤其喜歡坐擁現金，並利用市場回調來獲取資產。<br />\n<br />\n通常現金用途:<br />\n1. 回購<br />\n2. 股息<br />\n3. 再投資<br />\n4. 收購<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb05d1bf9fbb4783c49e9f879bc4baa172ee65ca","tid":1922603,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"巴郡或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cac37454f4efb3c42fe4b25ae1f230df4fe3c7","tid":1922603,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"google真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29371b960a3deb71bbe0bb5a5a93fd1992181117","tid":1922603,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"都要睇埋debt"},{"pid":"88336193ef6bafd18150e495cbbeb09175bdbe17","tid":1922603,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"除左第10要google<br />\n其他都識係咩公司"},{"pid":"c2030f4a064db45b83a3831d5acb545465ec4290","tid":1922603,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb05d1bf9fbb4783c49e9f879bc4baa172ee65ca","tid":1922603,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"巴郡或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"可以買投資騰訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a766f312626f9812dc129e7a1a6dd6f2056fd07","tid":1922603,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88336193ef6bafd18150e495cbbeb09175bdbe17","tid":1922603,